```{r, include = FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(
  collapse = TRUE,
  comment = "#>"
)
```

```{r setup}
library(imdbr)
```

Get the imdb id of "sherlock".
```{r}
get_id(name = "sherlock")
```

Get the overview information of "game of thrones".
```{r}
overview(name = "game of thrones")
```

Get crew information of "inception".
```{r}
top_crew(name = "inception")
```

Get characters' information of "interstellar".
```{r}
characters(name = "interstellar")
```

